        <div type="footnotes">
            <note xml:id="foot.f1"><ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_135.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">D. Appleton &amp; Co</ref>. published the third US edition of <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_6014.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Origin</hi></ref> (from the sixth London edition) in 1873; they may also have had on hand copies of the second US edition (from the fifth London edition), which was published in 1870.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f2">The London edition of <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_2400.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Expression</hi></ref> was published in November 1872, and the US edition in December 1872, although the date given on the title page is 1873 (<ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_2661.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Freeman 1977</ref>).</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">The US edition of <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1966.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Descent</hi></ref> was published in 1871.</note>
